Sunday, March 26, 2006
hey all! I had this dream and i wanted to see what you guys all thought... here goes...

ok a few nights ago i had a dream that involved my brother...
He and I were walking down a street in a trailor park laughing and playing around. we are at the time teenagers... and its all fun and giggles until he says to me... jas i have something to take care of and he begins to walk towards a drug dealer on the cornner and i am pleading with him to "lets go" and "come on lets go home" and i am standing infront of him pleading and he pushes me out of the way and hand the boy money and in return my brother is handed some drugs... at that moment in time everything freezes and i pick up my brother like i would a small child i am cradleing him in my arms and i begin to cry, i cry so hard and all i am thinking is i am taking him home... i awoke so sad and on the virge of crying...
... wow my dreams are very strange sometimes
your thoughts?

Sunday, October 09, 2005
 
Do u know what scares me?...

Growing into my womanhood..... growing older..... meeting the man I want to marry and have children with and being totally alone in doing so.. And when I mean alone I mean when a woman is going through the miracle of pregnancy and childbirth I know I would want my mother to be there for me as a loving supportive doting figure. I want my child or children to know a loving grandmother as I have. But I know for sure that when my time finally comes I will not have the love and support that I want and deserve from my mother. That is if she still alive when I am finally ready to have children. My mother is a selfish child in a 53 year old woman’s body.... and it scares me that one of the most important times in my life I will not be able to relate and commiserate or even hold hands with my mom...    I feel this emptiness in side this sadness that im the one left out... that i am being punished because drugs... and the  genetic mental problems have taken my mother away... though she is not dead... its something much worse...she lives in her own world... her world of fantasy... and darkness... she’s not my mom anymore... and I want to cry for our family’s loss.

<![endif]-->  <p class="MsoNormal">Hey so last night was the first night in a long time where I actually had a nightmare… I awoke Sunday morning at 6:40am rolled on top of all my blankets on my back arms above my head on the pillows… I remember going though the levels of sleep… until my eyes drifted open… until they were wide open… I remember no moving… that I was inquisitive first before I felt the chill of the dream… then it hit me and I sat straight up in bed breathing deep for a min… I didn’t know what to do… I didn’t feel like how I normally awoke from those types of dreams… I grabbed the phone… but there was no one to call… so I texted a friend… but like every other sane person in Santa Rosa he was a sleep lol… then I looked over the side of my bed and saw paper and a pen I grabbed it and started writing… my eye burned so I wrote half of it with my eye closed… the other barley open.. I felt I like I was in a trance… when I finished 40mins had passed by… but it felt as if may only 15 did.<span style="">  </span>Ok so here goes my dream…</p>  <p class="MsoNormal">It’s a 2 parter… part one…</p>  <p class="MsoNormal">The first thing I remember is that I walking along an ally way in an area in Tahoe there’s row house and theirs a soccer/baseball felid that butts up against the back of the houses im walking across the backyards with a man very tall and slender but hes mentally challenged hes my age but has the mental capacity of a 13 year old… in the dream I was his personal tutor but I was let go from the school and was told to stay away from my students but it wasn’t fair to them or me to just cut off that bond it would just end of reverting some of the children and some had made such improvement one such case was the boy I was walking with this night he loved me and we all new it but I was never unprofessional with him he understood my role in his life and we kept it at that. His sister on the other hand wasn’t to sure she was his legal guardian and he loved and looked up to her so much. During out nightly walks we would go through peoples throwaways and or junk to see what new things we could create.<span style="">  </span>He was into paint ball and was making an air powered shotgun lol to play with the other kids and he for me spare parts in the back yard of one of the houses… I on the other hand was looking to do some braking and entering one of these houses I use to work for in the sense that I worked very closely with one of my patients but when I was fired they kept some of my things like my winder jacket and running shoes so while he was looking through the junk I let myself in… I just about tripped over my shoes on the hallway… but I couldn’t find my jacket anywhere so I slipped out with only half of what I broke in for… the house was empty of people there was a town meeting going on this evening and most of everyone was there but then we heard a noise and it sounded as of people were arriving home so we began to run towards his house so that I may get him how with no one being the wiser <span style=""> </span>but his sister was on the back steps smoking a cig in the moonlight he was so happy<span style="">  </span>to see her… he introduced me so barley made the effort to shake my hand so was very protective of him she looked to be in her mid to late twenties kind of round with a no nonsense face. Her brother always talked about me as if I were an angel send down from heave to help him… she thought otherwise… anyways I had to keep moving before the people that were investigating the noises caught up with me so I continued on my way until I reach the town hall where I always seem to run to in any of my dreams that has this same street in it… after that …it fades to black…</p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><o:p> </o:p></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><o:p> </o:p></p>  <p class="MsoNormal">Part two.</p>  <p class="MsoNormal">Im in a car... it looks like an old land cruiser with the bare minimum no frills my grandmother is driving and were on a 3 lane road that is winding up a mountain to the right of me is the guard rail and drop off and to the left is the mountain rock and it seemed like a nice and quiet day… ya right… so this is going to sound a bit strange but we turned the corner and there on the street and on the cars passing by were clumps of human hair… almost like bundles… there were three colors blackish brown, <span style=""> </span>golden blond and golden strawberry blond…. It looked tike they were in sepia tones <span style=""> </span>and it shined in the sunshine so it was healthy hair… freshly cut… cars were sliding all over the place cars coming towards us heading down the mountain swerved into our lane and crashing into the guard rail and my Grammy had to hold hard to the stirring wheel to keep un in our lane… <span style=""> </span>as we drove on the hair trailed off but we did see a forest green Volvo that had smashed through the guardrail and was in a grass field there were other vehicles crashed on the side of the road I saw a medial van stopped on the side four women in lab coats were pulling out gurneys and I realized I new them and I asked for my Grammy to pull over that I wanted to help the wounded but there was no place to pull out of the way so we drove around the corner and we saw off to the side a studio apartment but all the outside walls were glass… she pulled in and ask me to grab supplies, water.. towels first aid kit she was going to go check things out while I found all the supplies… the house had one wall that separated the living space form the kitchen… everything in the house was furniture I remember growing up with from my grandmothers home… some pieces I know to be long gone… but everything was as it was when I was four and up. I opened the linen closet and grab some towels…. I found a gun… at first I wondered who would leave their gun there… so I <span style=""> </span>put it aside in the kitchen… I had a 2 way radio from the car incase my Grammy had information on anything… but I had it tuned into the police channel and I was listening to all of the horrified 911 calls coming in people screaming others saying there lost that they were thrown from the car and are lost in the woods… but they had their cell on them… that got me worried… like how many are out there how many have already died… and where was my Grammy… then I looked out the window and saw a man wondering down the side of the street…. Looking as if he was going to wonder into the woods instead of hugging the road… he had short black <span style=""> </span>hair about 6’3 green top with blue scrub pants all torn up and dirty he had no shoes or socks… and he was limping I got him inside and told him to sit down… but he didn’t look like he was listening to a word I was saying… then I saw another man limping towards the house he looked as if he had a purpose so I greeted him at the door he asked for some water and a towel when I went into the kitchen I could hear him dragging a chair… so I walked in and I saw him standing on a chair grabbing something from on top of a beam… I said most to myself… wow… you don’t look like your injured do…you… herd him smile under his breath… the injured man was gone… the man now standing on the chair had short golden blond hair with circle glasses <span style=""> </span>he was about 6’1 he looked like a classic nerd in the face but his body was well maintained… he had in his hands what looked like a projectile of some kind I was beginning to walk backwards when he smiled… so creepily I turned to run cause it was a small caliber and he was most likely to miss a moving target especially with a home made device. But I heard the shot and I felt it hit my spine between my shoulder blades I felt the searing hot pain begin there and start to travel, Spread through my back… and then I realized that it wasn’t a bullet but a trank dart… I felt the stuff go through my body so I slowed my breathing turned off none essential functions and heading for the door… I made it through and was trying to flag down a passing car but no one would stop they stared at me a blank stare that felt hallow… I started to trip a bit due to the drugs but I wasn’t going to give up on flagging a car from the streets… but it <span style=""> </span>was quiet for a moment so I walked out in to the lanes thinking that either I would be killed by a hit and run or I could continue walking to the safety of my Grammy… but with in a few seconds cars started passing me and other types of vehicles… like segways everyone was in a hospital gown people in car and on the other vehicles all the same short hair and hospital gowns… so I made it to the side of the street still none stopping… then I looked over and saw two people heading my way.. but something about them wasn’t right.. the man was black with dreadlocks but they were tied back he wore street clothing but nothing gansta jeans and a sweatshirt <span style=""> </span>which had blacks ,forest greens, and blues then the other was female cropped brown hair she looked nerves and she bit her nails as they came close to me she began to giggle to herself and he began to smile… I was dragging do to the drugs but I was still on my feet they began to circle me like to hungry sharks… I shadowed them with every step to keep them both in my sites… started to growl… as a primitive response to their smiles and giggles… I guess it was a primal reaction… then they lunged! Grabbing me by my wrists and laughing they kept pulling like they wanted to pull off my arms… I started yelling at this point in a British accent “turn the channel turn the channel, turn the fucking channel” I realized that I had entered my very own real life suspense film… and there was no way to turn the channel… so I pulled back my hand on the black man so that his arm was stretched out and I dug in my claws from his elbow to his wrist… he stopped laughing he grabbed me and pulled me in… and then I wake…</p>

<![endif]-->  <p class="MsoNormal">Hey so… after reading the books by Stephenie Meyer you know the…Twilight series… well even while I was still reading it I became tense, anxious, and a bit sad. And my reason was not due to what was happening in the book, but what was happening in side me… now I’m not some hormone driven 14 year old girl swooning over an imaginary guy… I know he’s a made up character but it saddens me because I wish even half of what he is in the book to be true for men in this world… but I know not to think like that or wish like that. because I know I will just be let down I have been taught to keep my expectations low so as to not be disappointed… however I wish… oh god I wish I could be pleasantly surprised in being wrong that there is a man out there with at least half of the qualities as Edward.. . and secondly be interested in someone like me… a long time ago I figured out what my type of man was and I new right away I would be disappointed because I new I would never get what I wanted… either he would have the personality I loved or he would have the physical features that made my knees go weak… <span style=""> </span>very few men have made me “swoon” in my life and maybe only 1 or 2 have been everyday guys… the rest I’m embarrassed to say are guys on the big screen… because it seems im attracted to men outside of me “class” and not necessarily class of wealth but in beauty and intelligence… I fine symmetrical faces beautiful, pronounced jaw lines hot… hands with the perfect balanced of strong and beautiful exciting, tall slender men to be graceful and handsome and men who have the intelligence to speak different languages, solve ridiculous math problems, right poetry but more importantly still have the patience and kindness to explain and possibly teach those to others without judgment to be breathtaking. <span style=""> </span>But I only look and take notice because thats all I will ever do… the men that I notice never notice me… now its not like I watch from afar and never take that step… I have… I must have a rather large set ( if you know what I mean*wink*) … to approach them but I have in the past… and they have always looked at me like I was nuts for even asking… and they would laugh or just say no… so I’ve learned to turn off that part of myself the area that hopes one day my affections would be returned by the right person and I had to remind myself of my class of beauty and brains… which is lower than the ones that I seek. Now im not saying im ugly either stupid or anything like that but im no prom queen, model, or straight A student… im average <span style="font-family: Wingdings;"><span style="">J</span></span><span style="">  </span>and so I gave up on falling in love “completely” I do love so please don’t mistake me I love my family and friends dearly and as for my serious relationships in the past I did love them to a point but I always felt I was holding back for something… waiting for it… for what it is… I don’t know… but i’ll know it when I have it… I bet this sounds nuts… <span style=""> </span>so for many years I have been looking at men from a different angle well for starters the men I was attracted to thought of me as a guy friend… lol or as my friends now call me “cool guy with tits” so I learned to adapt <span style=""> </span>and it was easy…im good at sports, im not dainty, and im often quicker as “yo mama” jokes than they are… and so when it came to that guy I sucked it up gave him the high five he expected and said good game or you really nailed the bastard there… and sad to say I would then lingerer silently <span style=""> </span>on the memory of his touch… now a days that’s a lot of who I am haha I mean I am the cool guy with tits and I enjoy it. But what this book did to me was it reopened the section that I thought I berried a long time ago… I had told myself that there is no such thing as complete love that it was a fairy tale and my logical brain believes this but my heart…my heart hopes for something different. Because anything less than that I would feel like I was settling for less than what I am for what I would give that right person. For that right person I would give all that I am… and if he was the right one he intern would give the same to me. <span style=""> </span>And I feel the pull, the pain, of wanting what I believe I will never find and I want to scream! And wish I had never read those books so that I could keep on believing that the person I would want to stay with should be kind to me… and is able to stand on their own 2 feet... you know the bare minimum … that’s one of the reasons why geeks are so alluring to me lol there so kind at heart *smiles* I love them for their hearts <span style="font-family: Wingdings;"><span style="">J</span></span> but there not the full package. Although I much rather spend my time with them then jokes or rebels or nerds lol silly I know to classify them but its… true lol and so I suffer in silence…once again… consciously restraining myself so that I will not be taken over completely by my dreams of that perfect person.<span style="">  </span><span style=""> </span>im going to have to re-stitch that part of my self that makes those dreams… make them seem so tangible… so right in my grasp...that when my dreams fail I know the pain of the real world would crush me… and <span style=""> </span>when I will finally settle down I’d know i could never be completely happy… GOD! I hate myself why do I have to have dreams… expectations? or feelings?... you know I haven’t felt these emotions… since… maybe high school… so over seven years I have had them under lock and key… or should I say needle and thread… and now its open and I feel as if the whole world can see me…and my weakness… and yes I consider wishful dreams that I know will never come true a weakness… for me at least… im suppose to be strong, focused, and realistic, not this hopeless romantic dreamer…( yanks out hair in frustration) <span style=""> </span>I keep being told that the love I wish for does not exist that im diluting myself that people don’t feel that way in real life… anyways I hope that getting this out of my head <span style=""> </span>well let some of the tension I feel go… and I hope in time the sadness fades. I just remember parts of the book and his I guess <span style=""> </span>I’d call it <span style=""> </span>his devotion to her it felt so true and complete that I… well… I was jealous… when Edward would say “my wife” or “misses Cullen” with what felt to me as complete joy and pride...I felt a stab of jealousy not because he’s (the character) not saying it to me or anything but the way he says it… with so much pride and admiration for her it was because I would want to hear that in the voice of the man I loved… and since I live in the real world as it were… <span style=""> </span>my chances of finding that are slim to none… sometimes I wonder if im even capable of loving someone completely.. . I don’t know… I’ve tried… when I thought I might be spending my life with Wyatt ( before he went all crazy) I tried to open myself up to him completely but I couldn’t…<span style="">  </span>it felt like there was a locked compartment<span style="">  </span>with in my heart.. and he didn’t have the right key to open it… I felt like a failure… or better yet that my brain was right that there was no such thing as loving someone completely but now … after reading those books… my heart says SEE it could happen… and my brain… well my brain has had no luck on telling my heart that its just a book… a fantasy… hmm some times I wonder that the reason why my heart holds out for that perfect person is because if there was no perfect person out there for me well then my heart would just give out now and stop beating to save its self from all the pain… you know?...i wonder if my making sense if others could understand me…</p>

hmm watching the movie Twilight for the first time this past week... reminded me of something... as i was watching the film i felt a sense of deja vu... and then it hit me.. the way the director plays up the blues in the film and how the greens are so pronouced... that is acatully the way i dream... my dreams always seem to have a blue filter on them and my dreams are so detialed that watching the film was like going home... strange i know...i wonder if others dream like i do...?... maybe i'll right more on this in a bit but first... its time to go get coffee with chris YAY its annoy chris time woot!

<![endif]-->  <p class="MsoNormal">Today.. my period started... but it wasn’t suppose to... my period has gone from being in between 25 and 23 days to being every 21 days to now...18... i don’t like where this is heading.... my mood swings are strong...I’m pretty sure i would be classified as legally insane during these times... its like someone flipped a switch...i want to go back to the old me... the not so angry or sad me...to a little bit after meeting Wyatt if i could have had a short relationship with him and if i was fine with that i think i would enjoy being that person more so than who i am now... i have alot of anger...life has been particularly unfair to me (i know i know woe as me)....in the past year i have lost a good friend... one i greave as though she has died and yet she still talks with my friends so its like everyone gets to have a relationship with her but me... i lost 2 aunties... those hateful bitches...i lost a guy friend... who i was close to...one of my best friends... lost her mother... and therefore i lost someone...i lost scout....poor kitty...:( i lost my job... i cant find another...my thyroid is dying... im allergic to wheat...my mother thinks im a drama queen that tells lies...hmmm is there anything else?... why... yes! yes there is.... im seeing someone.... and they found out their ill.... and most likely not long destined for this world... and for the first time tonight i saw that in his eyes...and it scared me... i would never let him see that but it did. i saw what the future lay ahead for him and for me...and the way he had treated me it was displaced anger and confusion from the state he was in.... hes independent but the way he was feeling he was needing some care and i was helping him but he wasn’t giving much to go on.... he had trouble waking up and im use to hypoglycemics.... like me so i kept asking if he needed food er something but no.... then after laying on my couch half a sleep for a while with me trying to keep  him awake... he sat up promptly and said.. i have to go he put on his shoes.... i couldn’t look at him.... i felt cheated...we were suppose to spend time together but he was so tired... and i know its not his fault its the illness but i cant help how i feel... anyways i couldn’t look at him it hurt to much so he leaned in and kissed my forehead and i sat on the couch ... he said he would text when he got home he did... all it said was "home" and that’s the last i have herd of him from tonight...so as a recap... loss of close friends...2 <span style=""> </span>loss adopted family...2 <span style=""> </span>loss in friend's family 1  loss of a pet 1 loss of jobs 1 loss of a parent knowing their child..1 health problems periods, thyroid and allergies...oh and "love life' …its not longed for this world.... so FUCK YOU WORLD!....i am a crab, my shell is impenetrable! What more pain do you want me to endure... why do you want me to endure it in the first place?... is it because you know i feel things, emotions more than others? Is it because i can appreciate colorful flavors of it? I SPIT IN YOUR FACE!</p>

everyone knows i'm in pain just about every day of my life... well most know that i do... but they almost never see it in my face... but its there... still  as i was sitting here at my computer reading my emails, updates and job listings i thought to myself... wow this pain is really getting to me.. and its only 4pm... and i awoke at noon so i have only been awake for 4 hours and i already need to take meds.... not a good sign... and then my process jump to when im in so much pain i cant get out of bed or walk correctly... more so when i have done some physical activity where it being walking for 3 hours, soccer for an hour, tickle wars that last until i start twitching or even sex. and i feel so sad because some times the lightest touch will send pain shooting up from the spot and it makes me so angry that in stead of feeling well exercised, healthy or well satisfied *wink* i feel pain and at points with my friends or past relationships  they have gotten very frustrated with me because when they would hug me i would yell out in pain or if i was being tickled i would get angry and lash out cause i wanted to escape the pain that was over whelming my system. and then i felt even worse because i hurt the person how was just trying to make me laugh :(  and sometimes i wish i had no physical contact with people so for one the pain would stop and secondly i wouldnt hurt others feelings by making them think that they're always hurting me its not their fault.. its me. but there are some good points for the first time in a long time someone was able to stroke my head in a light loving matter and it felt wonderful no pain! i had almost burst into tears! cause it had hurt for so long! and if he ever reads this... thank you:)
but anyways i guess im just going to have to come to terms with the fact that im going to have this... this wiring problem for the rest of my life and ya... its not as bad as it use to be thanks to Dr. Brian but hes not a miracle worker but hes made my life bearable now :) but you cant falter me for having low points right? i mean i'm only human... * raises eyebrow* or am I? teehee so instead of wining to my friends and getting on their nerves i'm writing it here... :) and hopefully this mood will pass through me by the time i end this note...

no matter how much pain i might be in i dont know if i could ever take my own life... i think i would miss al the beauty in this world way to much you know?

hey.... so its the day after valentines day... and all through my house.. is quiet. the couples are off doing things only lovers do my other roommates were off at work and so i was left in my house for the day. at first i didn't mind much i am still recovering from the epic flash mob pillow fight 2009... but then i realized that with out any distractions i was left with only you thoughts... not a good thing...

anyways i guess i'll just dive in.

hmmm well i have had a lot of bad things happen with me lately and its been real difficult to not think that  in some reason i deserved every piece of it.

i broke up with my long term boyfriend of 2.5 years he turned some of my family against me and i have had to take that loss and still move on. i feel as if i live in an alternate universe... i know this sounds completely nuts but right after everything happened losing Emma, kicking Wyatt out, losing my aunts deb and sand, i curled within myself for a long time... and i remember i believe 3 key point since then until the first week of December when i left for Tahoe and crystal's mom funeral... i remember my life wasn’t the same anymore and there was no big changes and yet everything was different when i came back to Santa Rosa colors were different and yet the same... like for example i remember a piece of furniture being one color but when i returned it was a different and yet it still had all the where and tear of the piece of furniture... or the thermostat was a different shape than i remembered but nothing was changed... i remember walking through my house noticing these tiny insignificant changes and feeling different inside like i was living a different life and yet my own at the same time....and i have kept this to myself until this moment for the fear of what others might think of me and my sanity.
so i keep living my life and feeling the difference in my life's currents and nothing more.
also i have begun dating... yes im actually dating i have gone on my first real dates and they have been great :) i have never known how it felt to be treated as the lady i am from a man my age. i have only had the respect from men my uncle and grandfather's ages... it had seemed to be that one had to be of a seasoned age to recognize a lady when they saw one.
hes my age which i rather enjoy because for once he’s actually older than me haha i don’t have to be the older one the "adult" i guess idk it seemed that when i dated someone younger than me they always saw me as the adult and i was just a young adult myself and i didn’t want the responsibilities that came with taking care of someone else no matter how strong the ties were or how much i did care for them... its in my nature to care for others... i really cant help it.
anyways he didn’t want to tell me his age because i believe since he is in high standings with respect with most people he knows no matter their age he doesn’t want anyone to know his true age because i think he then believes people would lose respect for him because he wouldn’t have earned the wisdom and respect that came with the age they thought he was . anyways so he says i bugged him into telling me his age...( i dont think thats completely true it wasnt that hard *wink*) so i found out he was closer to my age than i thought and it relaxed me because i was a bit disconcerted if i was attracted to someone more than 5 years older than I... i'd feel i was to immature for them.. like an annoying nat buzzing around someone’s face.... so that knowledge relaxed me a bit... but now when i mention it to me but more so for me because it reminds me when he says something I believe to be immature for his age I realized that no he’s my age its fine  and I only ever talk about it when its just us together  he gets upset because i know his real age. I see him as my equal but from the way he’s portraying his frustrations towards my comments about us being close in age it seems that he feels like instead of being by my side as an equal he would rather be above me in some way that if he was way older than me i would then automatically show him way more respect for his wisdom and strength.  What he doesnt know is that i do show him so much respect as is. but i think what hes looking for is what he use to have at his old job... at his job it seemed sometimes that he was god in more than a few peoples eyes and i think he misses that respect.  And if hes trying to find that admiration for him in me... its not going to happen. i feel alot of things for him love ( not sure what kind), respect, compassion, fear ( not form him but for him),  but above all i feel for him i like him i really do but im not sure hes going to be good for me...
his life was way different than mine in alot of ways but also the same in a few... but where we really split off is our past relationships... and i would be lying if i didnt say they intimidate me, i feel ill equipped to satisfy him now or in the future. and my deep routed insecurities arnt helping either. he doesnt really do Sexual monogamy and that was fine when we were friends but now were dating and of course i feel differently  about it but i dont feel i have any write to ask someone to change a way of life they have lived for as long as they can remember.  And for me Sexual monogamy is a must because for one i feel valued because that person has chosen to share their bed with me and only me. another is i feel safe no unexpected sexual encounters where i would have to worry that he caught something and intern gave it to me. and thirdly there always seems to be drama with the other encounters like jealousy, trust issues, ect ect. and thats why we have kept it casual you know? so from what im gathering  it was for my benefit  most of all because i seem to care way to much for people. but this past week he has been ill and i would stop by and check in on him if he wasn’t answering text messages or what not and he mentioned a friend of his was checking in a girl and i thought wasn’t that nice of her :) and then he showed me her picture and she was this adorable woman older than both of us but didnt look a day over 18... and i even thought damn if i was a guy i would do her lol anyways he then preceded to tell me they had a causal sexual relationship together im unsure how long maybe years but it had been a year since they had been intament anyways she had come over to bring him soup er something anyways she had asked if there was anything else she could help him with and he had said idk and then she jokingly asked hmm would it make you feel better if i walked around topless? and he laughed and said... a weak no.. and from what he told me her eyes got big and said what?! why not? and his answer was he then would be tempted to grab her and have his way with her and that his head was hurting to much to do so.....and what really sunk in was if i was in that situation i would have said thanks for the gesture but im kind of seeing someone but im a one on one kind of girl al the way. but what hurt was to him i wasn’t anything special enough to consider my feelings because he knows how i feel on the subject and that i am going out on a limb to try something new. but from the way it sounded if his head wasn’t pounding as hard as it was he would have jumped into bed with her without a second thought.... and im not sure he noticed me but my heart was struck just then... and it hurt... cause i dont think he would ever consider me special enough to consider my feelings that way. and so i laughed at his story and made jokes about doing her ect ect cause that’s what i do im considered the " cool guy with tits" because i can joke and hang with the guys and most often then not they dont see me as a girl... so i played the role... but in truth it hurt...but im learning to hid my emotions a bit... being a cancer i feel and am effected by them all the time!... and now when he doesnt text or call.... my mind wonders... who hes with is he enjoying himself? more so than he ever did with me... i agreed to a casual relationship with one condition if he does have other conquests that he has to inform me of them so that if they didnt use protection i can protect myself and so on... and now i wonder if he would tell me... something i have learned over the years is that im alpha female and i strive to fine an alpha male and hes pretty darn good *smiles*  but when you are an alpha female you want to protect your " territory" as it were so i do get jealous... its a normal reaction isnt it? but i dont ever say anything cause i dont want to be the jealous bitch i know i could be.  I don’t know if I should cut off the relationship now before I hurt worse or should I ride it out cause then I would have that experience and know and remember al the good time.. gut then there would be al the time I would be hurt and feel unworthy… maybe I need to talk with him… but these days hes either drugged out on med or ignoring my text messages… that another thing when were together…  I know he ignores text messages and calls from other girls but then I also wonder if he does that to me… and more often than not he thinks logical, without emotion just facts… well I wouldn’t say with out emotion I guess without consideration I think that if there was a possibility of him getting laid he would soon lock his phone in a drawer then to answer one of my texts… and maybe im thinking to highly of myself but i thought I was worth more than that.  I guess casual isn’t the right road for me…

hey guys... i thought i would type down a momentous occasion that happened on Saturday night... i went to my friend's amanda's sisters house warming party i didn't know many people there but since i was amanda's friend... i was cool. they gave me a glass of wine and i began chatting with her family... that was about 8pm when i had drunken 1 and half glasses of white wine amanda told me  i would have to drink for her too so her sisters husband hands me a shot of tequila.... my first one ever! and i downed that one... by the second one and my second tequila sunrise i was pretty well gone... and it was about 10pm i could NOT walk for the life of me i was swaying leaning up agenst the counter... and i was terribly slurring my words everyone thought i was so cute when i was drunk they said i sounded like a little kid, more relaxed having fun. lol  i think it was the 3rd huge shot that killed me... by that time i i was trying to talk to other and i could understand what they were saying and i could respond and i was told i made total sense the entire night it was just really hard to listen cause i was slurring so bad! but however me and this other fellow he was sober by the way we happen to be playing this hand slap game... and i kicked his ass while being drunk as a skunk! awesome!!haha and apparently i was having the best time texting my boyfriend's best friend and him about how drunk i was getting and but the middle of that night.. she was texting for me cause i still wanted to keep them informed... the cool thing was.. even when i was totally blitz... and i mean gone! i still understood that i could not drive or operate heavy machinery.. or even walk for that matter and i happen to call my aunt to inform her that her niece would be coming home totally out of it but that i was ok. :-p... i guess everyone had a great time watching me being drunk i was told they were laughing with me LOL ehh anyways oh oh i also kept asking to have someone take a picture of me because NONE of my friends were here to see me get like this.. you im the one who takes care of the ones who drink.... im never drunk! EVER! but no one had a camera :( sad day! anyway during one of my slurring rants.. that made sense by the way... i informed everyone that i had not cleaned my nose piercing out yet.. so amanda's sister's husband how wasn't that sober either got me to the sink... i was able to touch my nose with my finger just fine... and we got some salt and cleaned out my nose LOL it looked really funny....so it was all laughs and good times....  a guy form the party that amanda new... he played a hand slapping game... and i was totally snockered but i kicked his ass at it!! WOO WOO GO ME! then he leaned over and told me in my ear ( your naughty) amanda told him to do it.. its an inside joke cause i believe im a good girl but others seem to think im "naughty". so everything was going well...until that 3rd shot him me... and i new i was going to be sick.. i was informing everyone that i was a cheap date that its real easy to get me drunk.. they giggled. somehow i made it to the bath room... and well i got to see my sushi for the second time that day LOL... amanda was there making sure my hair was pulled back and i made the comment of hey look amanda did u know i had sushi today?!
